headline: Loop Capital sees tighter pricing at Dollar Tree, maintains cautious earnings view
summary: Investing.com -- Dollar Tree’s price advantage over competitors is narrowing, according to Loop Capital, which maintains a Hold rating and below-consensus earnings estimates for the company.

headline: Q1 Earnings Outperformers: Dollar Tree (NASDAQ:DLTR) And The Rest Of The Non-Discretionary Retail Stocks
summary: As the Q1 earnings season comes to a close, it’s time to take stock of this quarter’s best and worst performers in the non-discretionary retail industry, including Dollar Tree (NASDAQ:DLTR) and its peers.
